            +---------------------+
            |     main() starts   |
            +---------------------+
                      |
                      v
       +-----------------------------+
       | go sayHello()              |  -----------------------+
       | (Goroutine starts running) |                         |
       +-----------------------------+                        |
                      |                                       |
                      v                                       v
         +--------------------------+         +------------------------------+
         | fmt.Println("Hello from  |         | sayHello() runs in goroutine |
         | main")                   |         | prints: "Hello from Goroutine"|
         +--------------------------+         +------------------------------+
                      |                                       |
                      v                                       |
         +----------------------------+                       |
         | time.Sleep() allows        |<----------------------+
         | goroutine time to finish   |
         +----------------------------+

